rows.label: bf10240170_0010
rows.name:
All this data passed through me,
and I knew.

rows.label: bf10240170_0020
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: bf10240170_0030
rows.name: All of you...

rows.label: bf10240170_0040
rows.name: You were not in any way different from us, before.

rows.label: bf10240170_0050
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]--!!

rows.label: bf10240170_0060
rows.name: So, I left you alone.

rows.label: bf10240170_0070
rows.name:
500 years ago,
when the man finally arrived here...

rows.label: bf10240170_0080
rows.name: I did nothing when he took away Logos and Pneuma.

rows.label: bf10240170_0090
rows.name:
I stood and watched as Logos, instantiated into
Blade form, set out to purge the world.

rows.label: bf10240170_0100
rows.name:
You don't make sense!
Didn't you go to all that trouble to rebuild it?

rows.label: bf10240170_0110
rows.name: Then why would you-

rows.label: bf10240170_0120
rows.name: It is fate.

rows.label: bf10240170_0130
rows.name: Fate?

rows.label: bf10240170_0140
rows.name:
It is fated to happen.
It cannot but happen.

rows.label: bf10240170_0150
rows.name: My sins can never be atoned for.

rows.label: bf10240170_0160
rows.name: That can't be-

rows.label: bf10240170_0170
rows.name:
I had made my peace with it. Once more,
I longed for nothing more than to disappear.

rows.label: bf10240170_0180
rows.name: However...

rows.label: bf10240170_0190
rows.name: Something has now changed.

rows.label: bf10240170_0200
rows.name: And that is you, Rex. You and Pneuma.

rows.label: bf10240170_0210
rows.name: Me and...Homura and Hikari...?

rows.label: bf10240170_0220
rows.name:
You reforged your bond in a way I had not
thought possible. And the life you share...
